Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃猫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃猫大人  让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请享用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您还有什么别的需要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.67,0:00:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来有什么吩咐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:52.80,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(455,105)\fad(500,500)}「因为是桃猫大人的忧郁」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫也从围墙上摔下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃猫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为猫这还真是不合格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说刚才那不是很好的拍摄时机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我担心它有没有受伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说桃猫大人是好像有超强的生命力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是该说脸皮厚到让人肃然起敬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去完全没问题不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像心情很差
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有趣的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃猫大人  请就保持那样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它还真是悠闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做猫真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想每天无所事事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呢  变成猫的话好像就能够爬到很多地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍下各种有趣的照片了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去喝杯茶准备回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  走吧薰亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许叫我薰亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰亲～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你快给我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}真是太感谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:13.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不好意思  桃猫大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:28.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是野猪吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}请您无论如何帮帮忙！  桃猫大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:39.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}就交给我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:16.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}明明说了要你帮忙的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:16.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大骗子！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:19.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}笨蛋笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:23.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}回去吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:26.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}办不到办不到办不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在本町4丁目那一带好像又出现了野猪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 又出现了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易长成的蔬菜似乎被吃掉不少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  拍到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:47.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}住手  今天不要拍我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪  走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得桃猫大人没什么精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不和平时没什么两样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够无所事事还真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要有桃猫大人在就觉得松了口气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确  感觉它就是这一带的神兽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是超有存在感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃猫大人在的话就安心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  它动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪  走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和平时不太一样哎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  桃猫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟蹋农田的就是那只野猪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来讨伐它的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我不会向别人说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你拉钩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有肉球诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香亲  这真是偶然的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能说是前世就有的姻缘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运啊  Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…团子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这是勇者的肉球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是肉球…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很帅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:32.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帅的肉球…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看不见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香亲的话语一片混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊什么啊  纪惠我看见的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃猫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去感觉好像不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:50.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去还要准备小考啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫不要考试和上学还真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是轻松啊喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.25,0:11:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但猫也是很不容易的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再加「喵」玩猫语了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说顺嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:17.88,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(505,105)\fad(500,500)}「因为是失恋相机」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  HOBORO店主的什锦烧无论什么时候都是这么好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…的广岛菜啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,题目就定为「热情似火的冰冷瞬间」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.03,0:11:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光…临
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:02.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HOBORO烧…10个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10个？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您…是要带回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就现在在这里吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那那那那…那就给我来11个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就来12个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  那我就每人烧二十个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可要一·个·不·剩地给我吃完哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没问题  我还能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还早着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,标题「为了重新站起来」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么啦  只是被酱汁熏到…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:13:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚…肚子好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是何方神圣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是偶尔来竹原的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人小姐  我们马上就要打烊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚您在哪边住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居无定所的  没关系我露宿就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你在考虑些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没考虑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家现在没有多的铺盖  没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还能再吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别在这里吐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里是重要的建筑群保护地区
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐代美小姐  不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  之前和这女孩在朝日山见到过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:14:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是发生了什么啊  突然一个人开始大胃王比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正堂乡不管什么时候都是大胃王呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说塙同学  不要直呼以前班主任的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫  是认识的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有偶尔遇到过一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二楼的铺盖已经准备好了  你们慢慢来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得好香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事情了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我也睡这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  好期待过夜…贝类中牡蛎还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂乡  你给我回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了不要直呼我名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  得拜托理穗妹妹看家 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没问题  请不要管我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是爱逞强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白的那个人在你那过夜了？  真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  昨晚很晚才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况怎样  告白还顺利吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她早饭午饭都吃了很多  连甜点也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这豪吃的状态是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这边  注意脚下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳您费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻子  我在找你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚…肚子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  她好像是吃太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然吃那么多我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这量实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  给你们添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是小枫吧  之前我们见过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫保志真奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  她是飞田志麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是塙薰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:16:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫冈崎纪惠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是樱田麻音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说志麻子小姐的告白怎么样了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么  告白是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憧憬之路那天  志麻子小姐说是要向喜欢的人告白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那么  那之后告白成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…志麻子也算是努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然志麻子从初中起就一直就这么想着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对方说只把她当做朋友看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要自暴自弃  暴饮暴食啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许事实上他有无法对别人说的苦情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识的女性被谜之组织追赶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好一起逃到里约热内卢去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是里约…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:18:13.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}妄想力迸发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是实际上拒绝交往是因为他染指了坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就不想把她卷入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是装作对她稍微有点意思的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定都买好了保险  然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音  快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是有了妻子  无论如何也没法说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的  刚才我稍微一听
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都尽说些有的没的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你清醒着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧志麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  真奈美  你是特地来找我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:31.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我暂时去独自旅行了  bye
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你甩下一条那样的短信就不见了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我不担心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了  过去的事情就随他去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是今后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是要不要去好好玩一通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜风什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是开车来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要去准备开店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走  出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.04,0:19:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  坐上去  志麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很抱歉  大家就别跟来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要进行大人的恋爱谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就出发咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  快…快停…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔跑起来就无法停止  这就是恋爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要下去  我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱没有中途下车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.79,0:19:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每时每刻都加速装置全开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算一段恋情结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就正有活着的感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:42.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}前方禁止通行  请在这里返回
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果弄错了返回就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看  景色真好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉那小小的心灵创伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那家伙的照片  我全部都删了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一来到这里就感觉打起精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奈美  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来拍个重新振作的我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:21:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我来拍的话只能拍出悲伤表情的志麻子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻子一直都在逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻子拍下的照片瞒不掉你的真实心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明偶尔大哭一场就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤的时候  说出来又有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻子有多思念着他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传达了一份怎样的感情  我都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明可以向我宣泄感情的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奈美…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这孩子和我永远是志麻子的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奈美  你还是给我拍张照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍我这没用的哭丧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是没用呢  很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.04,0:22:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍下坦率而可爱的志麻子了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.18,0:22:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本该是悲伤的哭泣面庞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛在闪着炫目的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相机的不可思议又多了一个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.61,0:24:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  今天轻轻松松搞定20份
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.88,0:24:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  回到平常的志麻子了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.98,0:24:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原来不是暴饮暴食…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.16,0:24:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是本来就是大胃王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.29,0:24:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  玉响～hitotose～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.30,0:24:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「明天的我会是怎样的我…呢」
